title:
Instructions
On the stove, cook and drain the ground beef and sausage.
Add ground beef, sausage and remaining ingredients into the crock-pot
Cook on HIGH for 1 hour, stirring occasionally.
Serve on warm with chips and crackers.
directions: On the stove, cook and drain the ground beef and sausage.
Add ground beef, sausage and remaining ingredients into the crock-pot
Cook on HIGH for 1 hour, stirring occasionally.
Serve on warm with chips and crackers.
ingredients: 1 pound ground beef cooked and drained
1 pound ground pork sausage cooked and drained
10.75 ounces canned cream of chicken soup
10.75 ounces canned cream of celery soup
1 pound American cheese such as Velveeta brand, cut into squares
